lly, the accuracy of these cosmological predictions is\nassessed by comparing the analytical approximations with exact numerical\nintegrations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jul 2008 19:36:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 7 Jan 2009 15:44:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-07"}
